This paper is likely to belong to the category of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) as it deals with language modeling and subword analysis. It could also belong to Machine Learning (cs.LG) as it uses neural networks for modeling. Additionally, it could be categorized under Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) as it deals with natural language processing. Neural Networks (cs.NE) could also be a possible category as the paper uses them for modeling. Finally, Information Retrieval (cs.IR) could be a possible category as the paper deals with extracting information from text.
